Package ispd.arquivo.xml

Class IconicModelDocumentBuilder

java.lang.Object
ispd.arquivo.xml.IconicModelDocumentBuilder
public class IconicModelDocumentBuilder extends Object
Class responsible for manipulating xml files into iconic or simulable models, and building a document with a model from an iconic one.
